Package: wickrafeaturestore
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic ML-Ready Feature Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-feature-store over its C ABI hub: describe a
    feature spec once and fold OHLCV candles into a byte-identical feature
    matrix - the same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-feature-store
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-feature-store/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-feature-store C ABI shared library (WKFEATURESTORE_LIB)
    and its header (WKFEATURESTORE_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
